org.nd4j.linalg.api.iter

Class NdIndexIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nd4j.linalg.api.iter.NdIndexIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<int[]>

    public class NdIndexIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<int[]>
    Iterates and returns int arrays over a particular shape. This iterator starts at zero and increments the shape until each item in the "position" hits the current shape
    Author:
    Adam Gibson
